# Paste your Google Maps Platform API key here ("Maps JavaScript API" must be enabled).
# When set, the head unit uses Google Maps for 2D and 3D; when empty, it falls back to
# MapLibre/OpenFreeMap. The dev server restarts automatically when this file changes.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
 
# Optional: a vector Map ID from your Google Cloud console (enables custom styling).
# Defaults to DEMO_MAP_ID, which supports vector rendering and 3D buildings for testing.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_MAP_ID=